title: A1278 820-2936 not charging
message:
I have an A1278 820-2936 that it's not charging the battery.

I get 12.56V on F7040
12.56V on PPVBAT_G3H_CHGR_R

On U700 i get 4.6V in CHGR_ACIN

Can you help?

title: A1278 820-2936 not charging
message:
Do you get green light on Magsafe?
Did you test disconnecting BIL?

Post voltage and diode mode to ground at SCL/SDA lines of battery bus.

title: A1278 820-2936 not charging
message:

Diode:

Voltage:

title: A1278 820-2936 not charging
message:
Is the battery recognized at least?
Posy PPBUS_G3H voltage with both charger and battery connected.

Did you try known good battery?
